      "side": 1,
      "message": "[🔴 Critical] Line 2107: The new retry runs `startSync` only once after five seconds. If the DHT/account manager is still unable to announce after GSM standby, presence tracking can remain broken. Consider either retrying until success with bounded/backoff behavior, or explicitly invoking the identity announcement path that reports success/failure again. A single delayed `startSync` does not guarantee recovery from longer standby/network restoration delays.",
